    {
      "instruction": "<p>Rinse the <strong>quinoa</strong> in a sieve under <strong>cold running water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>quinoa</strong> to a pot with a matching lid with 250ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[500ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> and bring to the boil over a high heat</p><p>Once boiling, reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 15 min or until the quinoa is almost cooked</p>",
