    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the <strong>chopped parsley</strong>, <strong>capers</strong>, <strong>red wine vinegar</strong>, half <span class=\"text-danger\">[all]</span> the <strong>wholegrain mustard</strong>, 3 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[6 tbsp] </span><strong>olive oil </strong>and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> to a <strong>food processor</strong></p><p>Blitz into a smooth, thick paste – this is your <strong>super green</strong> <strong>salsa verde</strong></p><p>Tip: Cooking for 2? Save the remaining wholegrain mustard for another recipe!</p>",
      "order": 3,
