    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) over a medium-high heat with 1/2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[1 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>salmon fillets</strong>, season with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and<strong> pepper </strong>and cook for 8-9 min, turning once halfway, or until cooked through</p><p>Tip: Your fish is cooked through once it turns opaque and flakes easily</p>",
